a IR system with Naive Bayes classifier and EM algorithm:
(based on Text classification from labeled and unlabeled documents using EM
K Nigam, AK McCallum, S Thrun, T Mitchell - Machine learning, 2000 - Springer)

usage: 
	$./compile.sh
	$./naivebayes.sh -option1 value1 -option2 value2 …
		or
	$./EM.sh -option1 value1 -option2 value2 …

	options:
		-i data-directory
			path of data containing 3 directory, train, unlabeled and test
		-o outputfile-path
			output file
		-n labeled-data-size
			the number of labeled documents in each class the program uses